longBusinessSummary: Go Green Global Technologies Corp. operates as a water and fuel technology licensing, marketing, manufacturing, and development company worldwide. The company, through its wholly owned subsidiary, Go Green Technologies Corp., provides solutions utilizing the proprietary patented Sonical technology for non-chemical water treatment and fuel combustion applications. It offers Sonical Water Treatment System for food, coffee, home and restaurant, pharma, and other industries, including paper, textile, electronics, petrochemical, plastics molding, glass trade, and tanneries; and Sonical Fuel Charger, an electro-physical device, which is installed in the fuel supply circuit feeding motors, burners, and boilers that are used in cars, trucks, boats, and boilers. The company was founded in 2009 and is based in Monroe, Connecticut.
